% We have the following options available
%  1. linkcolor   - red       - internal links
%  2. anchorcolor - black     - anchor text
%  3. citecolor   - green     - bibliographical cirtations
%  4. filecolor   - cyan      - url to open local files
%  5. menucolor   - red       - adobe menu items
%  6. runcolor    - filecolor - run likns
%  7. urlcolor    - magenta   - linked urls
%
% We really only use 1, 3 and 7. Among them 7 is external link and
% the rest are internal. Almost the entire index consists of
% "internal link"s. So it must be a dark colour specially pleasant
% to the eye.



